168
00:09:51.583 --> 00:09:54.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Did we fall out of our story
into someone else's story...

169
00:09:55.083 --> 00:09:55.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
again?

170
00:09:56.875 --> 00:10:00.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Silly. It's<i> all </i>our story.

171
00:10:01.125 --> 00:10:04.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I hope I get to live long enough
to find out how it ends.

172
00:10:06.958 --> 00:10:09.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[scratching]

173
