198
00:13:33.500 --> 00:13:36.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[whooshing]

199
00:13:38.167 --> 00:13:39.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please!

200
00:13:39.917 --> 00:13:42.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
