[clattering sounds]

202
00:14:05.917 --> 00:14:07.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[doors clanks]

203
00:14:14.292 --> 00:14:17.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Take my hand!

204
00:14:28.000 --> 00:14:29.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Please!

205
00:14:54.333 --> 00:14:56.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
